  "handNote": {
    "lettering": "Deeply cut letters of a regular, fairly square module, without serifs. Alpha with straight bar, standard delta, straight epsilon with equal bars, heta rectangular closed top and bottom, standard lambda, nu slants to the right, xsi in form of X, omicron of standard size, pi with shorter right hasta, four bar sigma with equal open strokes, phi with large eye and vetical stroke of equal size not over-extended.",
